="min-w-0"><h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Import Customizations</h1><div class="fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-2 animate-in duration-300"><div class="flex h-full flex-col"><header class="mb-6"><p class="mt-2 max-w-prose text-pretty text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Already set this Mac up by hand? nixmac can scan for tweaks that aren't in your flake yet — macOS preferences, Homebrew casks and taps, launch agents — and turn them into code.</p></header><div class="flex-1"><div class="relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl rounded-tl-3xl rounded-br-3xl rounded-bl-3xl border border-transparent shadow ring-1 shadow-black/10 ring-white/5"><div class="pointer-events-none mask-radial-to-90% mask-radial-at-center" style="position: absolute; inset: 0px;"><canvas width="722" height="343" style="display: block; width: 722px; height: 343px;"></canvas></div><span class="relative z-20 mx-auto mt-8 flex size-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand/10 text-brand ring-1 ring-brand/30" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-radar size-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19.07 4.93A10 10 0 0 0 6.99 3.34"></path><path d="M4 6h.01"></path><path d="M2.29 9.62A10 10 0 1 0 21.31 8.35"></path><path d="M16.24 7.76A6 6 0 1 0 8.23 16.67"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"></path><path d="M17.99 11.66A6 6 0 0 1 15.77 16.67"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle><path d="m13.41 10.59 5.66-5.66"></path></svg></span><div class="relative z-20 flex flex-1 flex-col items-center px-6 pt-6 pb-8 text-center"><h3 class="text-balance font-semibold text-xl">Scan this Mac for untracked settings</h3><p class="mt-2 max-w-md text-pretty text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Already set this Mac up by hand? We'll run a few read-only commands to detect what you've customized and turn it into code. Noth