 stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></span><div class="flex flex-col text-left"><span class="font-medium text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground">Import Flake</span><span class="text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs leading-tight">Import your configuration</span></div></button></li><li><div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg px-3 py-3 transition-colors bg-sidebar-accent" aria-current="step"><span class="mt-0.5 flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-medium tabular-nums transition-colors border-primary bg-primary text-primary-foreground">4</span><div class="flex flex-col text-left"><span class="font-medium text-sm leading-tight text-foreground">Import Customizations</span><span class="text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs leading-tight">Capture existing tweaks</span></div></div></li><li><div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg px-3 py-3 transition-colors"><span class="mt-0.5 flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-medium tabular-nums transition-colors border-border text-muted-foreground">5</span><div class="flex flex-col text-left"><span class="font-medium text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground">AI Inference</span><span class="text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs leading-tight">Hosted or your own key</span></div></div></li><li><div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg px-3 py-3 transition-colors"><span class="mt-0.5 flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-medium tabular-nums transition-colors border-border text-muted-foreground">6</span><div class="flex flex-col text-left"><span class="font-medium text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground">First Build</span><span class="text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs leading-tight">Apply your configuration</span></div></div></li></ol></div></aside><main